reviews.review_text:
What a recording! Truly amazing recording.  Just superb.  

I used to have a cassette copy of this show back in the early 1980s, but it wasn't this recording.  

This is the bomb.

Thank you.

Most intense rider I have ever witnessed  This was really a great show and a very hard ticket to get on April fools day. Me and my 5 friends were lucky to get 4 seats 8th row left center between Jerry and Bobby. Chinacat was semi short but terrific and Jerry smiling a lot. The rider was another story, the intensity level rose exponentially, Jerry was playing at a ridiculous level and we were dancing and falling over each other. Especially a 5:30, jerry really nails it, and Belushi comes out of no where and does this flip in front of jerry. Jerry was so animated and smiling during this insane rider, I wish more deadheads could have experienced it. After the last note of rider, me and my friends all collapsed onto each other and weren’t able to get up until Stella blue. We couldn’t even move for the other one, which we never ever sit for. 39 years after this show I still blast this rider and it brings me right back there in front of jerry with him smiling and looking so amused at what was happening. RIP Jerry,  dentaldogbill
